dct_description_sm: Color legend includes "pastoral leases," "Pastoral Blocks open to application," "Agricultural and Grazing Land (a large portion of this land is suitable for Horticulture)," "Unoccupied Pastoral Land."

Waterways, various place names (bays, mountain ranges, towns), roads.
